ed="T" n="0781c07"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0781c07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000014963">縉雲連雲院</placeName><persName key="A010592">有緣</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0781c08"/><persName key="A010592">釋有緣</persName>，俗姓<name><anchor xml:id="beg0781sgsz8"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>憑</sic><corr>馮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0781sgsz8"/></name>，<placeName key="PL000000035550">東川梓潼</placeName>人也。小學之年往<lb
ed="T" n="0781c09"/><placeName key="PL000000034767">成都福感寺</placeName>，事<persName key="A010594">定蘭</persName>開士<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1319"/>，即<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>師矣。隨侍<lb
ed="T" n="0781c10"/>出入，多在內中。一旦宣召，<ref type="person" target="#A003667">帝</ref>以筆書其衫<lb
ed="T" n="0781c11"/>背云：「<ref type="person" target="#A010592">此童子</ref>與<ref type="person" target="#A003667">朕</ref>有緣」，由茲召體<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1601"/>矣。<date from-iso="+0855-01-26" key="j20333682033751" to-iso="+0856-02-13"><name>大中</name><lb
ed="T" n="0781c12"/>九年</date>，遇<persName key="A010596">白<roleName>公</roleName>敏中</persName>出鎮<placeName key="PL000000034805">益部</placeName><ptr target="#n1635"/>，開戒壇，即於<lb
ed="T" n="0781c13"/><placeName key="PL000000034714">淨眾寺</placeName>具尸羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g904"/>也。續於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京輦</ref>聽習經律五<lb
ed="T" n="0781c14"/>臘。後身披布褐，手執墨勅，海內遊行。參見<lb
ed="T" n="0781c15"/><persName key="A010597">小馬神照</persName>，凡同時叢林禪祖無不禮謁者。<lb
ed="T" n="0781c16"/>乃居<placeName key="PL000000057100"><anchor xml:id="beg0781005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>除</sic><corr>滁</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0781005"/>州<anchor xml:id="beg0781sgsz9"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0781sgsz9"/>山</placeName>，及南遊至<placeName key="PL000000018271">武夷山</placeName>，時廉使<lb
ed="T" n="0781c17"/><persName key="A010598">李誨</persName><ptr target="#n1636"/>為築禪室。<date from-iso="+0876-02-03" key="j20410462041399" to-iso="+0877-01-21"><name>乾符</name>三年</date>，至<placeName key="PL000000015019">縉雲龍泉大賽<lb
ed="T" n="0781c18"/>山</placeName>立院。因奏祠部給額，號<placeName key="PL000000015022">龍安</placeName>。勅度七<lb
ed="T" n="0781c19"/>僧，住十八載。安而能遷，止<placeName key="PL000000014963">連雲院</placeName>焉。太守<lb
ed="T" n="0781c20"/><persName key="A010599">盧約</persName><ptr target="#n1637"/>者，以諶諒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1602"/>之誠，請入州<placeName key="PL000000057107">開元<anchor xml:id="beg0781sgsz10"/>寺<anchor xml:id="end0781sgsz10"/></placeName>別院，<lb
ed="T" n="0781c21"/>四事供施焉。<date key="j20524812052481" when-iso="+0907-05-27"><name>天祐</name>丁卯歲四月八日</date>，示疾，至<lb
ed="T" n="0781c22"/><date key="j20525332052533" when-iso="+0907-07-18">六月朔日</date>終于廨署，報齡七十三，臘五十二。<lb
ed="T" n="0781c23"/>遺旨囑制置<persName key="A010600">揚習</persName>司空主喪務，於寺南園<lb
ed="T" n="0781c24"/><anchor xml:id="beg0781006"/>茶<anchor xml:id="end0781006"/>毘。火滅，散分舍利數百粒。後收四十九<lb
ed="T" n="0781c25"/>粒并遺骨一缾，瘞于石塔。<date from-iso="+0946-02-10" key="j20666202066973" to-iso="+0947-01-29"><name>晉</name><name>開運</name>三年乙巳<lb
ed="T" n="0781c26"/>歲</date><ptr target="#n1638"/>，<persName key="A010595">文泰<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>撰塔碑焉。</p>
